Comment: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:10.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.40,0:29:14.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}See the bunny bees and puffs of steam from singing kettles in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.09,0:29:25.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}Red butterflies with forks and knives ,who like to make a meal of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.83,0:29:36.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}Life is clockwork quick lightning slow faster on your toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.77,0:29:48.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}So eat your sugared dream and face the day before it runs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.40,0:29:14.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}从树上嗡嗡叫的蜂巢看到小蜜蜂和一阵阵气流
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.09,0:29:25.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}红色的蝴蝶拿着刀叉好像在吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.83,0:29:36.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}生活就像闹钟一样在你舌尖流失
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.77,0:29:48.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}在他溜走之前 那就品尝着你美味的梦面对着那一天
Comment: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:10.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\pos(297,60)}英国 伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 雨果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,随时恭候 安洁莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,穿透吧 穿透吧 水滴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,敲打吧 敲打吧 钢铁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,切断金色麦穗 挽起石臼 潜入夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的手转动水车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让前往之物流向应往之所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 送给恩滋华斯和他的弟子智世
