Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(275,2520)\pos(642,686)}{\c&HFDFFFF&\c&H59A819&)\fn方正中雅宋_GBK\fs36\b1\bord0\shad0\c&HFDFFFF&\3c&H59A819&\fsp15\pos(650,569.429)}{\blur30\t(0,1390,0.3,\blur0)\b0}等待繁星之人\N{\fs25\fsp0}【中篇】
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1975,2520)\pos(642,686)}{\c&H59A819&)\fn方正中雅宋_GBK\fs36\bord2\shad0\c&HFDFFFF&\3c&H59A819&\fsp15\pos(650,569.429)}{\blur50\t(0,1390,0.5,\blur3)}{\c&HFDFFFF&\1a&HFF&\b0\3c&HA25C07&}等待繁星之人\N{\fs25\fsp0}【中篇】
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到森林图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我是森林的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不对  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么说  我只是想让你安心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那些家伙是进不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你看得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那你能解释自己为什么能看得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  做了坏事的家伙是进不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说是不允许进来才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都热衷于读书  不会伤害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,找个地方坐下  慢慢地享受时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有合适的书籍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这里好久都没人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这里能有你喜欢的书就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说找一本会喜欢你的书才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:07:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,擅自跑进来  非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事情完全不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,稍…稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  应该是在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就这个好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫理一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦理一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鸟…智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鸟智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.40,0:08:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,借书证
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为了能回到这里  记得要带好借书证
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了  出去之后要径直跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧  跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸我可累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我说  和别人说话的时候能别玩手机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,别玩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了稍微等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都这样  完全把我的话当耳边风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我每天都是怎么过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  我也是很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,反正都是她的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在全是我在照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,当初是你没多加考虑就说收养她  所以她才会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时不也同意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那还不是因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰  听话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大辉  你也赶快去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你要来我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.48,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都因为你  妈妈才…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小姑娘  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\fs30\c&H334055&\frz122.1\pos(376,495)}暑假作业②读后感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我能来看书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,借书证有带着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有这张借书证
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是本馆的使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,随时都能前来  也可以借阅书籍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是每次仅限一本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还有就是进出时要随手关门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要遵守了这些规则  每天都能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,每天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  每天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可以尽情地阅览
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到森林图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我家真的已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  老婆带着孩子都搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我家已经照顾够久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这回该轮到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你也完全喜欢上书了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  看书的时候可以忘记一切烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  羽鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话  一直待在这里也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没想好写哪本书的读后感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明明读了那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为都很有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么书?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那本是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一直都放在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那本是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想  是一本什么样的书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那选哪一本好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:18:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阅读书的最后一页
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.31,0:18:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,读后感还…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不早点回去的话  妈妈不会担心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人会担心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为阿姨都搬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  这都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老在意那些怪东西  经常惹阿姨生气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就今天这次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,仅限今天  下不为例
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,能让你写出读后感的书
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那一天我就是不想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是少见  智世居然会如此固执
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为当时我还是个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,路兹  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你不痛苦就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  然后呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然后  那一夜就成了特殊的一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我有本书想送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,「孤零零的小星星」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,连环画
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你一定需要这本书
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  能帮我收拾一下这里的书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,「孤零零的小星星」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在漆冷的虚无夜空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有一颗小星星在那里独自发着光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,日出前 一定要把她送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:24:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  你再也无法进来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.16,0:25:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.24,0:25:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.26,0:25:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.73,0:25:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.20,0:25:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你还能进来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.72,0:25:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.98,0:26:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.12,0:26:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你关门了吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.13,0:26:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.43,0:26:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.40,0:26:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这本不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.82,0:26:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.09,0:26:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.53,0:26:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.58,0:27:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.80,0:27:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.03,0:27:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.16,0:27:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.89,0:27:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.13,0:27:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这本书借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.76,0:27:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真…真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.11,0:27:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,记得一定要还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.48,0:27:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.16,0:27:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.55,0:27:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.29,0:27:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.55,0:27:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.56,0:28:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心  它们都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.28,0:28:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.16,0:28:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我没忘记关门的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.36,0:28:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鸟智世  我有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.68,0:28:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能把这本书送到某人手中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.85,0:28:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我已经做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.22,0:28:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.64,0:28:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.36,0:28:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,三浦!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.17,0:29:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,未能遵守的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.40,0:30:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,身负青年的遗恨
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.41,0:30:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,少女奔跑了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.74,0:30:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,向着未知的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.95,0:30:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真弓…
Comment: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:10.76,Comment,,0,0,0,,
